description:
Winter is the six-part spin-off TV series of the Australian TV movie The Killing Field. Rebecca Gibney stars as Detective Sergeant Eve Winter.




Winter - Season 1, Episode 1



Detective Sergeant Eve Winter leads the task force assigned to investigate the murder of young 23-year-old mother Karly Johansson at Rocky Point, a hauntingly beautiful fishing town south of Sydney.



Original Air Date: 04-Feb-2015
